<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>actually...</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Stridar">Stridar</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 4:09 a.m. 4/6/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> actually...<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=2131" TARGET=_self>Re: RaceWar server</A> (Jackal)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>Think about this. Would a would a dwarf warrior and a troll warrior who worshipped the same god get along? No. The Dwarf warrior would think it was his duty to rid the world of Trolls. And well a Troll would see a nice dinner. But what I am getting at is just cause they worship the same race doesn't mean they believe others have a right to. A Half elf Paladin might hate Humans. Maybe his elf mother got raped by a human. Now to him a human would not have the right to worship the same god as him, and it would be a great thing to have them all wiped from the earth. Of course I see a problem here. Where do half elf paladins start off in life? Freeport or Qeynos. Going to be tough for some half elf that start off in humans city's to get much done. I am hoping Verant thinks about this and changes it some for this server.

<P>&gt; Though I think this is away for better roleplaying, it still
<BR>&gt; leaves something to be desired. Shouldn't a Human Paladin be
<BR>&gt; able to kill a Human Shadowknight? Shouldn't a Erudite
<BR>&gt; Necromancer join up with a Gnome Necromancer and kill paladins?
<P>&gt; Though race war is good, but not enough.
<P>&gt; IT should be deity war. Imagine, the good gods, fighting the
<BR>&gt; evil gods? A Half-elf paladin fighting a human paladin doesn't
<BR>&gt; seem right, because they follow the same god.
<P>&gt; The war should be based on Dieties, not races. If two different
<BR>&gt; races follow the same god, do you think the god would be happy
<BR>&gt; if they killed each other? No, I don't think so.
<P>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
